card.title: The "Virginia Model" Fraud

_source.content:
VA was rigged like every other state. incl the Gov race:
@LadyDraza predicted the vote. vote distribution followed the North Dakota model
https://rumble.com/v11rd4t-the-virginia-model-fraud.html

"Virginia Model: Flipping blue states or securing RINO spots?":
https://rumble.com/v17jagy-virginia-model-flipping-blue-states-or-securing-rino-spots.html

They track who votes during early voting and they use ERIC, so they know everything about you before you get there and they know who you'll vote for. Then they send in phantom ballots to match votes they don't like and that games the hand count.
